rComments: Good prof. Posts many detailed notes on blackboard and thoroughly answers questions. I agree with the other rating that the material is dry sometimes, but the clarity of her explanations is very good.

This is the worst class I have ever taken. The subject matter is extremely dry and the professor is very hard to follow in class. Her notes are extremely disorganized and her knowledge of the course material seems shallow at times. I did not enjoy her attempts to make the course interactive as constantly asking students for answers only wasted time
